---
import LegalPage from '@/components/legal/LegalPage.astro';
---

<LegalPage
  title="Accessibility | Black Knight Roofing"
  description="Accessibility information and support contacts for the Black Knight Roofing website."
  heading="Accessibility"
  intro="Black Knight Roofing wants this website to be usable by as many people as possible. If you have trouble accessing any part of the site, contact us and we will work to help."
>
  <p>
    We aim to present website content in a clear and usable way for visitors seeking information about roofing,
    exterior services, inspections, financing, and service-area availability.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
  <p>We are working to support accessible browsing and customer communication by:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Using readable page structure, headings, links, and form labels</li>
    <li>Providing contact options by phone and email if a digital interaction is difficult</li>
    <li>Reviewing issues that are reported to us and making reasonable updates where appropriate</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    This statement is a general accessibility commitment. It does not represent a claim that the website has been
    audited, certified, or proven to meet any specific accessibility standard in every respect.
  </p>

  <h2>Need Help Accessing Content?</h2>
  <p>
    If you have difficulty using this website, accessing a form, reading content, or requesting information, please
    contact us and tell us:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The page or feature you were trying to use</li>
    <li>What issue you encountered</li>
    <li>How you would like us to follow up</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Accessibility Contact Information</h2>
  <p>
    Email us at <a href="mailto:support@blackknightroofing.com">support@blackknightroofing.com</a> or call
    <a href="tel:17208040571">(720) 804-0571</a>. Our standard business hours listed on this website are Monday through
    Friday, 9am to 5pm.
  </p>

  <h2>How We Handle Requests</h2>
  <p>
    When an accessibility issue is reported, we review the concern, determine what follow-up is needed, and make a
    reasonable effort to provide assistance or improve the affected content.
  </p>

  <h2>Related Pages</h2>
  <p>
    See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>, <a href="/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>, and
    <a href="/company-info">Company Info</a> pages for additional information about the website and our business.
  </p>
</LegalPage>
